quoteText: If Airbnb undertakes or is involved in any merger, acquisition, reorganization, sale of assets, bankruptcy, or insolvency event, then we may sell, transfer or share some or all of our assets, including your information
title: The service can sell or otherwise transfer your personal data as part of a bankruptcy proceeding or other type of financial transaction.
